<H2><A NAME="SECTION021140000000000000000">
3.1.4 GetBonds</A>
</H2>
<dl><dd><pre class="verbatim">
virtual OESystem::OEIterBase&lt;OEBondBase&gt; *GetBonds() const
virtual OESystem::OEIterBase&lt;OEBondBase&gt; *GetBonds(
  const OESystem::OEUnaryPredicate&lt;OEChem::OEBondBase&gt; &amp;) const
</pre></dl>

<P>
Return an OEBondBase iterator of the bonds connected to an atom.  The
returned iterator traverses only the explicit bonds that are attached
to the OEAtomBase.  The number of bonds in the iterator is identical
to <code>OEAtomBase::GetExplicitDegree</code>.

<P>

